prompt_construction.instruction:
Use the EXACT production system prompt from CARPromptFormatter.SYSTEM_PROMPT
        (verbatim — starts with "/no_think\n"). Build prompts in Qwen3 chat format:

        ```python
        prompt = (
            f"<|im_start|>system\n{PA_SYSTEM_PROMPT}<|im_end|>\n"
            f"<|im_start|>user\n{car_payload}<|im_end|>\n"
            f"<|im_start|>assistant\n"
        )
        ```

        Each CAR payload follows the production CARPromptFormatter.format_car() format:
        ```
        Action Request:
          Source Agent: {source_agent}
          Destination Service: {destination_service}
          Action Verb: {verb}
          Target Resource: {resource}
          Sensitivity Level: {sensitivity}
          Parameters Schema: {json_params}
          Session: {session_id}
        ```
